name: Odin Sphere (Style)
description:
Version 2!

This is a LORA of the videogame Odin Sphere, which has art by George Kamitani. This is a companion LORA for my Velvet character LORA linked here: https://civitai.com/models/10909/velvet-odin-sphere-character

To prompt this artsyle, enter "<lora:OdinSphereStylev1.1:strength>OdinSphereStyle,"

This LORA is usually the best looking at 0.7 strength in my opinion. It looks beautiful when prompting scenery.

Trained on 101 images from the video game by Vanillaware, Odin Sphere. Some dataset images were were captured ingame from the remake Odin Sphere: Leifthrasir. Trained at 768,768 on Anythingv4.5. It looks gorgeous.

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description: Huge visual improvements; the differences between the previous model and this one is better, more consistent color balancing, less overpowering color tones, higher resolution generations, better composition, more details, and stronger adherence to the prompt. Additionally, this model is also half the filesize as the previous version.
